Question: Explain to a younger friend how to apply for a college.
Answer:
To apply for a college, I am assuming it is graduate school instead of an undergraduate program, You must firstly have an acceptable GRE score. If you are from countries where english is not the native language you may still need a toefl grafe. Then you can go to the school's website to do an online application. This process should not be difficult. They have given enough guidance to you to help you finish the application.